						Flags
                                        -e = selects on processes on a system, regardless of wether they are associated with the current users terminal session
					-v = verbose mode (gives notification of task complete)
					-r= delete
					-i = interactive
					-p = creates directories including the parent directory
					-a = do not ignor hidden files
                                        -f = displays full formating list of the process including process ID (PID), Parent Process ID(PPID), CPU, Memory usage, start time, command names
